  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691990/extras/0fc88d8af32fb22e5d6f87e8092909a6.poster.avif?t=1684277836\" width=500 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691990/extras/0fc88d8af32fb22e5d6f87e8092909a6.webm?t=1684277836\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691990/extras/0fc88d8af32fb22e5d6f87e8092909a6.mp4?t=1684277836\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Units can be freely converted into combatants or workers according to your strategic needs. As long as you have enough equipment!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691990/extras/dffdaf3e699b09113a38041f29ef63cd.poster.avif?t=1684277836\" width=500 height=376 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691990/extras/dffdaf3e699b09113a38041f29ef63cd.webm?t=1684277836\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691990/extras/dffdaf3e699b09113a38041f29ef63cd.mp4?t=1684277836\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Give your units the role of workers by crafting equipment that can gather resources.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691990/extras/5e6846f578bddefb0c2753b482156be7.poster.avif?t=1684277836\" width=500 height=376 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691990/extras/5e6846f578bddefb0c2753b482156be7.webm?t=1684277836\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691990/extras/5e6846f578bddefb0c2753b482156be7.mp4?t=1684277836\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Stop the monsters from attacking with the combatants and go out to recover the stolen items through the cracks.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691990/extras/f87b9240608f3037b369f92b883031ac.poster.avif?t=1684277836\" width=500 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691990/extras/f87b9240608f3037b369f92b883031ac.webm?t=1684277836\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691990/extras/f87b9240608f3037b369f92b883031ac.mp4?t=1684277836\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>As you gather resources, you can build equipment or buildings for combatants that require more resources.<br><br>Choose an appropriate upgrade by establishing an appropriate response strategy according to the enemy's attack type.",
